      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E92 M3 featuring the legendary S65 naturally aspirated V8. This high-revving powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing to deliver a linear power band up to its 8,400 RPM redline. The 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a variable M differential lock that ensures precise torque distribution across the rear axle. The chassis retains its factory-spec kinematics, offering the communicative feedback of a hydraulic steering rack and a well-sorted multi-link rear suspension. Recent preventative maintenance includes a specialized focus on the rod bearings and throttle actuators, ensuring this high-performance machine remains mechanically robust for its next owner.",
